Package: xserver-xorg-input-wizardpen
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, xserver-xorg (>= 7.3)
Recommends: easystroke
Description: WizardPen graphics tablet support
 WizardPen dvices are often manufactured by Waltop and similar
 companies and then often re-branded.
 .
 This package provides X.Org grahpic tablet support for
 (among others) the following devices:
  - Acecad Flair II GT-504
  - DigiPro 5.5×4” Graphics Tablet
  - Digital Ink Pad (A4 format)
  - G-pen
  - Genius Wizardpen, Genius Mousepen,
    Genius Easypen i405, Genius
  - iBall, iBall Tablet PF8060,
  - Manhattan
  - Pentagram
  - QWare
  - Trust TB-3100, Trust TB-5300, Trust TB-6300
  - UC-LOGIC
  - AIPTEK HyperPen 10000 U (and similar)
 .
 Not all AIPTEK graphic tablets are WizardPen devices. See also:
 xserver-xorg-input-aiptek in case this driver won't work.
